\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b nocturna}: Plant usually fairly sparsely pubescent below. Calyx-teeth usually triangular-acuminate or lanceolate and acute. Filaments glabrous. Seeds 0·5-0·7 mm, blackish. 2n = 24. {\i Throughout the range of the species}.
